RealTimeResultGroupDefinition.SqlString: SELECT Port.Name AS 'Port Name', AllDevice.Name AS 'Device Name', IgmpRouterResults.McastCompatibilityMode AS 'Multicast Version', IgmpRouterResults.RouterState AS 'Router State', SUM(IgmpRouterResults.TxFrameCount) AS 'Tx Frames', SUM(IgmpRouterResults.RxFrameCount) AS 'Rx Frames', SUM(IgmpRouterResults.RxUnknownTypeCount) AS 'Rx Unknown Types', SUM(IgmpRouterResults.RxIgmpCheckSumErrorCount) AS 'Rx IGMP Checksum Errors', SUM(IgmpRouterResults.RxIgmpLengthErrorCount) AS 'Rx IGMP Length Errors' FROM AllDevice, Port, IgmpRouterResults, IgmpRouterConfig, RelationTable WHERE ( RelationTable.Type = 'AffiliationPort' AND RelationTable.SourceHnd = AllDevice.Handle AND RelationTable.TargetHnd = Port.Handle AND IgmpRouterConfig.ParentHnd = AllDevice.Handle AND IgmpRouterResults.ParentHnd = IgmpRouterConfig.Handle AND IgmpRouterResults.IfHandle = IgmpRouterConfig.IfHandle AND AllDevice.DataSetId = @DataSetId AND Port.DataSetId = @DataSetId AND IgmpRouterResults.DataSetId = @DataSetId AND IgmpRouterConfig.DataSetId = @DataSetId AND RelationTable.DataSetId = @DataSetId ) GROUP BY IgmpRouterResults.IfHandle
